metadata.name: Wheel of Fortune (Tarot Series)
metadata.description:
· WHEEL OF FORTUNE ·

Chance. Cycles. Flexibility. A positive (or negative) omen. Oftentimes this foreshadows an incoming stroke of luck, a turning point, or a hard pivot. The elements are forever in motion; no one is exempt from the turning of the tides.
